data.meta_description: Roy Wilhelms Estherville – Services for Roy Wilhelms, 74, will be held Tuesday at 1:30 p.m. at the Henry-Olson-Fuhrman Funeral Chapel in Estherville with Pastor Rick Capps officiating.
